*   [08-Tiloca-Coordinating the Use of Application Profiles for Ephemeral Diffie-Hellman Over COSE (EDHOC)](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/125/materials/slides-125-lake-coordinating-the-use-of-application-profiles-for-ephemeral-diffie-hellman-over-cose-edhoc-00) - **Marco Tiloca**

